{"tid":2102304,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】議會抗爭必勝方法！集中本土票源，踢走舊泛民","createTime":"2020-07-10T11:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T14:44:47.000Z","uid":202076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"162eac4cc2440ff3f313d630d80ddd3e723ff6fe","tid":2102304,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"點樣可以令更多本土派入閘踢走泛民？<br />\n<br />\n泛民黃big暈、dead body之流嘅政績，過往香港人已經有目共睹，正如新東論壇入面，鄒家成所講：「我哋嘅目標唔再係本土、泛民、建制三分而天下，而係議會入面只有抗爭派同保皇黨。」<br />\n<br />\n四年前，大家話有得投，一定會投返本土，所以我希望參加初選嘅本土派，每一位參選人，我哋都唔可以放棄，全部都要入閘，踢走舊泛民。<br />\n<br />\n問題：我留意到連登有個論述係要放棄某個本土派，而將票源集中喺一至兩個人身上。<br />\n<br />\n原因係如果本土派喺全都要嘅情況下，有機會互相介票，反而減低入閘機會，咁不如放棄一兩個本土派確保選情穩陣啲。<br />\n<br />\n但我哋點解要用呢種方法，去放棄某啲本土派嘅人？我要所有本土抗爭派一齊入閘，一個都不能少，進入議會抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n建議：所以初選需要按返地區配票，避免票王出現，先可以令更多本土派入閘，為咗令票源更加平均，我哋首先根據每位候選人嘅票源來自邊一區，再按唔同區合資格選民嘅人數，分析再加以協調而得嘅數據。<br />\n<br />\n所以，大家只要按照自己嗰區投返本土派嘅參選人，泛民已經有鐵票支持，所有支持初選嘅年青人都應該集中返票源，票投本土！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOaUbMX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOaUbMX.png&h=828ff69d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64dRYr1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64dRYr1.png&h=654212dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99xGBdJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99xGBdJ.png&h=53e7c283&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbAdsks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbAdsks.png&h=66f2d816&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNLAFFv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNLAFFv.png&h=ecc899f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f9b765f71e5c326c21d9cf0d8868dd5387ee502","tid":2102304,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81c7e31c12d755c28a3ac7261185c5f1759a30cd","tid":2102304,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:13:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41ac12c5fb26559a2bac9e7c0800e3ab03b3f991","tid":2102304,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:14:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"343043d113f547287bb5940308818de674dcf831","tid":2102304,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41546c8e5fd9e8aad282778b39be2c64d2b2ed8d","tid":2102304,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88cd6506bbcd77b8ba9d86be0d6417b151357379","tid":2102304,"uid":204214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:19:01.000Z","msg":"其實應該要好似班建制咁配票 先可以確保所有抗爭派入到閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114be5ea105fbab2d0f343fd40d3b2cadd2305aa","tid":2102304,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"幾時黃之鋒列入本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4cd4bb6ef14fe107cdcb13f382b5f13642c16a","tid":2102304,"uid":204214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42d8273a8c6997c1e1e9c078dc9bc3372a27b89f","tid":2102304,"uid":204214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eff303c04595b9beeed4e640c3266abde49e6d51","tid":2102304,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"114be5ea105fbab2d0f343fd40d3b2cadd2305aa","tid":2102304,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"幾時黃之鋒列入本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:41:33.000Z","msg":"民主黨都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a82a8dddd71446098209b89da52af