x/i/0o1we4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0o1we4c.png&h=e89433b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2BXaCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2BXaCx.jpg&h=f8d1cadc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df507a6cf05df6054ee35db4d87ffac1007e8084","tid":2102304,"uid":86127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"推到有人見到！"},{"pid":"14a2d32952daba7f9976779f82347247b582b18e","tid":2102304,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:44:47.000Z","msg":"九龍西如果完全照你方法配票，由石硤尾邨、南昌邨到美孚新邨呢啲人口咁密集嘅地方全部投曬馮達浚，分分鐘張崑陽都會墮馬，然後馮達浚會變九西朱凱迪嘥曬啲本土票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}